<F P=103> FL0804014294 </F>
<F P=104>  Havana Cuba Vision Network </F>
<F P=105>  Spanish </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] In a solemn ceremony, Commander of the Revolution 
Juan Almeida Bosque, vice president of the Council of State, 
received His Excellency (Augustus Kuesi Yankey), who presented 
his credentials as Ghana's extraordinary and plenipotentiary 
ambassador to Cuba. Foreign Vice Minister Isabel Allende was 
also in attendance. 
  The Ghanaian ambassador was accompanied by advisers (Francis 
A. Segat), and (Paul Wenton Keshirt). 

